-- Emirates NBD $500 mln perpetual bond launched at 6.375 pct 
-- By Archana Narayanan
-- Wed Sep 10, 2014 07:14AM EDT
-- None



DUBAI, Sept 10 (Reuters) - Emirates NBD <ENBD.DU> (ENBD), Dubai's largest lender, launched a $500 million, Tier 1 capital-boosting bond at 6.375 percent, a document from lead managers said.

Pricing guidance for the perpetual bond had been given in the area of 6.5 percent earlier on Wednesday. The order book closed in excess of $1.3 billion. Allocations and pricing were to occur later on Wednesday afternoon.